cs.HC, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.LG, cs.CY 

The paper focuses on a context-aware mobile app recommender system and its deployment with real users, which involves aspects of human-computer interaction (cs.HC), information retrieval (cs.IR), and social and information networks (cs.SI). The paper also discusses the evaluation metrics and machine learning techniques used in the system, which relate to machine learning (cs.LG) and cryptography and security (cs.CY).
